[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000001_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000001_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "Harker affected no surprise at all-he looked the astonishment he felt as the younger man rose and motioned him to the comfortable easy chair which he himself had just previously taken.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "\"Dear me!\" he exclaimed, nodding his thanks.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "He took the chair which Bryce drew forward and pulled out an old-fashioned cigar case, offering it to his companion.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "\"Genuine stuff that, sir-I've a friend in Cuba who remembers me now and then.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "No,\" he went on, as Bryce thanked him and took a cigar, \"I didn't know you'd finished with the doctor.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "\"You know it?\" inquired Bryce.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "\"I come down to see him now and then-I've been here since yesterday.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000007_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000007_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "Stopping long, doctor?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "\"I'm off tomorrow morning-eleven o'clock,\" said Harker.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "The two travellers sat talking until bedtime-but neither made any mention of the affair which had recently set all Wrychester agog with excitement.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "But Bryce was wondering all the time if his companion's story of having a friend at Barthorpe was no more than an excuse, and when he was alone in his own bedroom and reflecting more seriously he came to the conclusion that old Harker was up to some game of his own in connection with the Paradise mystery.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "\"The old chap was in the Library when Ambrose Campany said that there was a clue in that Barthorpe history,\" he mused.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "\"I saw him myself examining the book after the inquest.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "No, no, mr Harker!--the facts are too plain-the evidences too obvious.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000012_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000012_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "I'd give a good deal to know what Harker really is doing here-and who his Barthorpe friend is.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000013_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000013_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "And at that hour Simpson Harker, who had breakfasted before nine, was in close consultation with his friend-that friend being none other than the local superintendent of police, who was confidentially closeted with the old man in his private house, whither Harker, by previous arrangement, had repaired as soon as his breakfast was over.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000013_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000013_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "Had Bryce been able to see through walls or hear through windows, he would have been surprised to find that the Harker of this consultation was not the quiet, easy going, gossipy old gentleman of Wrychester, but an eminently practical and business like man of affairs.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "Put your best plainclothes man on to him at once-he'll easily know him from the description I gave you-and let him shadow him wherever he goes.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000014_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000014_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "And then let me know of his movement-he's certainly on the track of something, and what he does may be useful to me-I can link it up with my own work.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000014_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000014_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "And as regards the other matter-keep me informed if you come on anything further.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000014_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000014_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "Now I'll go out by your garden and down the back of the town to the station.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000015_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000015_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "He was not going to draw any attention to himself by asking questions of present day inhabitants, whose curiosity might then be aroused; he knew better methods than that.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000015_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000015_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "Every town, said Bryce to himself, possesses public records-parish registers, burgess rolls, lists of voters; even small towns have directories which are more or less complete-he could search these for any mention or record of anybody or any family of the name of Braden.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000015_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000015_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "And he spent all that day in that search, inspecting numerous documents and registers and books, and when evening came he had a very complete acquaintance with the family nomenclature of Barthorpe, and he was prepared to bet odds against any one of the name of Braden having lived there during the past half century.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "The man who had spent a very lazy day in keeping an eye on Bryce, as he visited the various public places whereat he made his researches, was also keeping an eye upon him next morning, when Bryce, breakfasting earlier than usual, prepared for a second day's labours.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000016_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000016_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "And there he pursued his tactics of the day before and went straight to the vicarage and its vicar, with a request to be allowed to inspect the parish registers.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000016_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000016_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "The vicar, having no objection to earning the resultant fees, hastened to comply with Bryce's request, and inquired how far back he wanted to search and for what particular entry.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "\"Perhaps you will kindly lend me this book for an hour?--then, if I see anything very noteworthy in the index, I can look at the actual registers when I bring it back.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "The vicar replied that that was precisely what he had been about to suggest, and Bryce carried the book away.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000020_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000020_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "On the third page he saw the name Bewery.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "But the follower, knowing his man was safe for an hour, was in the bar outside eating bread and cheese and drinking ale, and Bryce's surprise was witnessed by no one.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000022_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000022_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "A name so uncommon that here-here, in this out of the way Midland village!--there must be some connection with the object of his search.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000022_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000022_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "He turned to page three hundred eighty seven with a sense of sure discovery.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "And there an entry caught his eye at once-and he knew that he had discovered more than he had ever hoped for.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "june nineteenth eighteen ninety one.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "Twenty two years ago!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000025_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000025_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "But john Brake who married that Mary Bewery-who was he?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000025_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000025_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "Who indeed, laughed Bryce, but john Braden, who had just come by his death in Wrychester Paradise?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
