        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "And-what did it all mean, and imply, and what bearing had it on Braden or Brake's death?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000026_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000026_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "And his lunch done, he set off for the vicarage again, intent on getting further information, and before he reached the vicarage gates noticed, by accident, a place whereat he was more likely to get it than from the vicar-who was a youngish man.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "\"Are you the Charles Claybourne mentioned there?\" he asked, without ceremony.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "\"That's me, sir!\" replied the old shoemaker briskly, after a glance. \"Yes-right enough!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "\"How came you to witness that marriage?\" inquired Bryce.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "The old man nodded at the church across the way.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "\"Do you remember this marriage?\" asked Bryce, perching himself on the bench at which the shoemaker was working.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000033_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000033_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "\"Twenty two years since, I see.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000034_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000034_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "\"Miss Bewery's marriage?--why, of course!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
