        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000041_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "Bruce assimilated all this information greedily-and asked for more.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "\"I'm interested in that entry,\" he said, tapping the open book.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000042_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000042_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "\"I know some people of the name of Bewery-they may be relatives.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000043_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000043_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "The shoemaker shook his head as if doubtful.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1049_133454_000044_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1049/133454/1049_133454_000044_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1049",
        "content": "\"I remember hearing it said,\" he remarked, \"that Miss Mary had no relations.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
